A Starbrand. A Nightmask. A Justice. A Cipher. They are manifestations of god-like power on Earth, chosen by the Universe. In the conclusion to the first arc of this RED-HOT new series, four newly-ascended super humans must accept their new existences...and survive those who would exterminate them.,2007,5
32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99
